from wordcloud import WordCloud
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np
# 한글 폰트 설정
plt.rcParams['font.family'] = 'Malgun Gothic'
# 유니코드에서  음수 부호설정
plt.rc('axes', unicode_minus=False)


wc = WordCloud('./NanumGothic.ttf',
               background_color = "white",
               max_words = 100,
               stopwords = stopwords)
wc = wc.generate(word_c) # str자료만 가능, list자료는 안됨
plt.figure(figsize = (12, 12))
plt.imshow(wc) #interpolation = "bilinear")
plt.axis("off")
plt.show()

okt=Okt()
words=okt.nouns(df2['키워드'][0])

words1=[]
for i in df2['키워드']:
    tmp=okt.nouns(i)
    words1.append(tmp)
words1

words1=sum(words1, [])
str_words=' '.join(words1)

#단어 세기
counter=Counter(words1)

#한글자 추출하기
# tmp=[]
# for w in words:
#     if len(w)==1:
#         tmp.append(w)
# print(tmp)

word_one=[w for w in words1 if len(w)==1]

#단어 리스트에서 한글자 빼기
words1=[i for i in words1 if i not in word_one]


str_words1=' '.join(words1)

#단어 집계
str_words2=str_words1.split(' ') 
top=50
cnt = Counter(str_words2)
top_=cnt.most_common(top)

# 단어집계 데이터프레임으로 바꾸기
df5=pd.DataFrame(top_, columns=['단어','개수'])

#단어제거
fillter=((df5['단어']!='마을') &(df5['단어']!='기업') &(df5['단어']!='지역'))
df5[fillter]

df5[fillter].set_index('단어').plot(kind='bar', figsize=(15,5))
plt.grid()
